WEBVTT

00:16:58.287 --> 00:17:00.442
and because the song has a payment system

00:17:00.466 --> 00:17:01.928
in the sense of bank account,

00:17:01.952 --> 00:17:04.300
all the money flows back to the artist,

00:17:04.324 --> 00:17:06.559
and they control the industry,

00:17:06.583 --> 00:17:08.995
rather than these powerful intermediaries.

00:17:09.757 --> 00:17:10.908
Now, this is --

00:17:10.932 --> 00:17:15.124
(Applause)

00:17:15.604 --> 00:17:17.301
This is not just songwriters,

00:17:17.325 --> 00:17:18.824
it's any creator of content,

00:17:18.848 --> 00:17:20.315
like art,

00:17:20.339 --> 00:17:22.807
like inventions,

00:17:22.831 --> 00:17:25.792
scientific discoveries, journalists.

00:17:25.816 --> 00:17:28.829
There are all kinds of people
who don't get fair compensation,

00:17:28.853 --> 00:17:30.323
and with blockchains,